library(tidyverse)
library(tidytext)
library(dplyr)
df<- Data
head(df)
df <- separate(df, normalized_date, into = c("norm_month", "norm_year"), sep = " (?=[^ ]+$)")
dim(df)

textDf <- df %>% 
 unnest_tokens(word, text) %>% 
  anti_join(stop_words)
Joining, by = "word"
head(textDf)
sent_df <- textDf %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("bing")) %>%
  count(wikipedia_title, sentiment, sort = TRUE) %>%
  filter(wikipedia_title != "?") %>% 
  ungroup()
Joining, by = "word"
sent_df %>%
  group_by(sentiment) %>%
  slice_max(n, n = 10) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(wikipedia_title = reorder(wikipedia_title, n)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(n, wikipedia_title, fill = sentiment)) +
  geom_col(show.legend = FALSE) +
  facet_wrap(~sentiment, scales = "free_y") +
  labs(x = "Contribution to sentiment",
       y = NULL)

bing_word_counts <- textDf %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("bing")) %>%
  count(word, sentiment, sort = TRUE) %>%
  ungroup()
Joining, by = "word"
bing_word_counts
bing_word_counts %>%
  group_by(sentiment) %>%
  slice_max(n, n = 20) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(word = reorder(word, n)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(n, word, fill = sentiment)) +
  geom_col(show.legend = FALSE) +
  facet_wrap(~sentiment, scales = "free_y") +
  labs(x = "Contribution to sentiment",
       y = NULL)

box <- df %>% 
  filter(title == "THE MURDERS IN THE RUE MORGUE") %>% 
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>% 
  anti_join(stop_words)
Joining, by = "word"
plot_sent2 <- box %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("nrc")) %>%
  group_by(sentiment, word) %>%
  count(mycount = n())
Joining, by = "word"
ggplot(plot_sent2)+
  geom_bar(aes(x = sentiment, fill = sentiment))

adv_fic <- df %>% 
  filter(classification == "Adventure,Science_fiction") %>% 
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>% 
  anti_join(stop_words)
Joining, by = "word"
plot_sent <- adv_fic %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("nrc")) %>%
  group_by(sentiment, word) %>%
  count(mycount = n())
Joining, by = "word"
Pest <- df %>% 
  filter(title == "KING PEST") %>% 
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>% 
  anti_join(stop_words)
Joining, by = "word"
plot_sent3 <- Pest %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("nrc")) %>%
  group_by(sentiment, word) %>%
  count(mycount = n())
Joining, by = "word"
ggplot(data = plot_sent, aes(label = word)) +
  ggrepel::geom_label_repel(
    aes(x = word, y = rnorm(nrow(plot_sent)),
        label = word),
    direction = "both", 
    box.padding = 0.04,
    segment.color = "transparent", 
    size = 3) +
  facet_wrap(~sentiment, ncol = 2)+
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(),
        axis.text.x = element_blank(),
        axis.ticks = element_blank(),
        panel.grid = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_blank())

ggplot(data = plot_sent2, aes(label = word)) +
  ggrepel::geom_label_repel(
    aes(x = word, y = rnorm(nrow(plot_sent2)),
        label = word),
    direction = "both", 
    box.padding = 0.04,
    segment.color = "transparent", 
    size = 3,
    max.overlaps = 50) +
  facet_wrap(~sentiment, ncol = 2)+
  labs(x = "", y = "") +
  theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(),
        axis.text.x = element_blank(),
        axis.ticks = element_blank(),
        panel.grid = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_blank())

ggplot(data = plot_sent3, aes(label = word)) +
